# Black Bean Burger

Based on [https://www.washingtonpost.com/recipes/...](http://web.archive.org/web/20211023023225/https://www.washingtonpost.com/recipes/black-bean-burgers/15322) ([archive](http://web.archive.org/web/20211023023225/https://www.washingtonpost.com/recipes/black-bean-burgers/15322))

